    against RecArray.
- Release 2.1.0
  * Added Structure and "structure expressions" to support
    structured arrays.
  * Added RecArray.
- add skip-pyright-tests.patch
- Expand use_system_packages.patch
  * Don't build the wheel a second time in tests, the
    `invoke wheel` command fails otherwise.

